N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 261.7 - Applicability of article 21

Nothing in this Part in connection with group or mass merchandising policies shall be interpreted as exempting any person from the applicable licensing requirements of Insurance Law article 21. Notes
